Descriptions: A man standing next to the sink in his bathroom. He is holding a toiletry bag.
A man is sitting on a couch holding a cup of water.
A person is sitting on a couch with a foot on the table in front of his. The person has both hands on the foot which is on the table.
A person is reading a manual for something while sitting on a couch.
A man is sitting on a couch. In the table in front of him, he has laid out a flannel on which he has put both his hands on.
A man is sitting on a couch while trying to take out a piece of tape from the roll of tape that he is holding in his hands.
A man has his left foot on a chair and is looking inside a cupboard in his kitchen.
A man is sitting on a couch with a pen in his hand. There are textbooks to his right so he might be studying.
A man is bent double in his living room looking for a tennis ball, which is under a couch, that he appears to have lost.
A man is sitting in a chair in his room and has thrown a tennis ball across the room.
Two women are walking next to each other on a field of grass while a man a close way away is walking at a right angle to them on the same field.
A women is sweeping dead leaves on the ground with a broom. A man on her left is watching her. A women is seated down at a table and is also watching the women sweep.
A man is holding the cap of a torch while sitting on a couch.
A man is sitting on a couch while folding an orange shirt.

Third people, two men and one women, are standing around a table. One man is standing in front of a cutting board with a sliced apple on it with the women standing next to him. The other man has a kitchen knife in his hand.
A man is sitting on a couch in his room. He is holding a pillow as if he is about to throw it.
A man is cleaning a table with a cloth. Two women are sitting at another table in the background.
A man is sitting on a couch. He is holding a small piece of paper in his hand. There is a bowl on the table in front of him which is full of folded pieces of paper.
There seems to have been an accident on a road involving a biker and a car. The biker seems fustrated with the person driving the car. The bike is on the floor.
A man is sitting on a couch. He has bands wrapped around the tips of his fingers.
